text: Congophiloscia annobonensis is a species of land crustacean isopods, in the family Philosciidae. The species was named by Helmut Schmalfuss and Franco Ferrara in 1978. The species is endemic to the island of Annobón in Equatorial Guinea. ==References== Category:Woodlice Category:Endemic fauna of Annobón Category:Invertebrates of Equatorial Guinea Category:Crustaceans described in 1978
title: Congophiloscia annobonensis
